name: blog
description: [Clean Blog Jekyll](https://startbootstrap.com/themes/clean-blog-jekyll/) is a stylish, responsive blog theme for [Bootstrap](https://getbootstrap.com/) created by [Start Bootstrap](https://startbootstrap.com/). This theme features a blog homepage, about page, contact page, and an example post page along with a working contact form powered by [Formspree](https://formspree.io/).
